description: Golden Band Resources Inc. explores, development, and extracts gold ores in Canada. Its portfolio consist of 13 gold deposits and 5 former producing mines covering an area of approximately 870 square kilometers and are located in Star Lake, Decade, Komis, and Jolu. Golden Band Resources Inc. is based in Saskatoon, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Paul Frederick Saxton B.Sc. (Eng), M.B.A., P.Eng., PEng
